You've got them mixed up.

01:45.856 --> 01:49.233
You're making
a mistake.

01:49.359 --> 01:52.737
You're making a mistake
with the reindeer.

01:52.821 --> 01:54.822
Tsk, tsk, tsk.

01:57.826 --> 02:01.913
Would you mind stepping out
for a moment? Open the door.

02:06.794 --> 02:08.502
I'm sorry. The store
isn't open today. I'm just-

02:08.586 --> 02:11.506
I don't want to buy anything, and
I'm sorry to interrupt you in your work.

02:11.590 --> 02:14.675
But I wanted to tell you
you're making a rather serious mistake.

02:14.802 --> 02:16.844
Huh?
With the reindeer, I mean.

02:16.929 --> 02:19.055
You've got Cupid
where Blitzen should be.

02:19.139 --> 02:22.809
And Dasher- Oh, Dasher should be
on my right-hand side.

02:22.935 --> 02:25.144
He should, huh?
Yes. Yes.

02:25.229 --> 02:29.607
Oh, and another thing. Donner's antlers
have got four points instead of three.

02:29.691 --> 02:32.360
Still, I don't suppose anybody
would notice that except myself.

02:32.486 --> 02:34.529
Nah, I don't suppose so.
No.

02:34.655 --> 02:36.197
Well, bye.
Not at all.

02:36.323 --> 02:38.407
Thanks.
Glad to have helped you. Bye.

02:38.492 --> 02:40.618
Dear, dear.

02:46.250 --> 02:49.043
